<event name="BOSS_TEXT_2">
	<text>You chase down the Flagship and discover it is heavily damaged from the previous fight. Scans indicate that it has redirected considerable power to its drones. Get ready for a fight.</text>
	<status type="clear" target="player" system="sensors" amount="100"/>
	<choice hidden="true" req="loc_negotiation" lvl="0" blue="false" max_group="0">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Flagship might be weakened, but it is still formidable. Keep up the fight!</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK_FLAGSHIP"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="loc_negotiation" lvl="1" blue="false" max_group="0">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>Suddenly, a small automated vessel breaks off from the fleet in the distance. You receive a hail from the shuttle. "Hello. This is an automated message sent from Admiral Vance of the Rebel fleet. We have taken into consideration your past victories, and the considerable damage you have already dealt to the Flagship. With this in mind, the Rebellion no longer holds interest in this reality. We offer our surrender."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event>
					<item_modify>
						<item type="scrap" min="2000" max="2000"/>
					</item_modify>
					<win ach="peace" creditsText="credit_victory_peace" text="" creditsBackground="VICTORY_PEACE"/>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="BOSS_TEXT_3">
	<text>You're not certain how it's able to keep fighting with the amount of damage it has sustained. It looks like it's transferred power to defensive systems as well as... some kind of super weapon. Be prepared... this is it!</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<loadEventList seeded="false" first="true" generate="true" default="COMBAT_CHECK_FLAGSHIP">
				<event name="BOSS_TEXT_3_GNOME" req="chaos_mode" lvl="1"/>
				<event name="BOSS_TEXT_3_VANCE" req="loc_vance_betrayal" lvl="1"/>
			</loadEventList>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="BOSS_TEXT_3_GNOME">
	<achievement>ACH_GNOME_FAIL</achievement>
	<playSound>gm_fail</playSound>
	<loadEventList seeded="false" first="true" generate="true" default="COMBAT_CHECK_FLAGSHIP">
		<event name="BOSS_TEXT_3_VANCE" req="loc_vance_betrayal" lvl="1"/>
	</loadEventList>
</event>
<event name="BOSS_TEXT_3_VANCE">
	<text>As you approach the Flagship for a third time, an ASB shot flies past your ship and nearly collides with the Flagship. In the distance, the Rebel forces have turned amongst each other. It appears as though word of Vance's betrayal has caught on, and it's created a schism in their forces. Expect additional fire support during this final stretch!</text>
	<environment type="PDS" target="enemy"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK_FLAGSHIP"/>
	</choice>
</event>
	
<event name="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_1">
	<text>"So, you can invade the homeworlds of some barbaric aliens and convince them to turn against themselves. That is nothing compared to the mission of our movement! We seek to bring peace to galaxy. I doubt you know anything of peace."</text>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_orchidcruiser">
		<text>We saved the Orchid Gardenworlds from a pirate siege.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_2"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_mfkgunboat">
		<text>We saved an entire city and memorial from a siege put on by the Rebellion.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_2"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_autodread">
		<text>We came to an alliance with the Primal Reaper by helping them repel one of your assaults.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_2"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_clancruiser">
		<text>We saved the last of an endangered alien species from the EHG.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_2"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_hacker">
		<text>We liberated an entire civilian sector from the hacker clan.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_2"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_crew_dianesh">
		<text>We managed to convince the Crystalline Empress herself to be open to the rest of the galaxy.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_2"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>The Rebellion is not peaceful! The Federation is what's bringing peace to the galaxy.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The commander laughs. "Oh, how pitiful. To bring peace, there must first be war! The Rebellion will rid of the dangerous xenos of each reality. I tire of this conversation. There will be no peaceful resolution to this confrontation." He cuts comms, and the Flagship continues to charge its weapons.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK_FLAGSHIP"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_2">
	<text>"And how might have you accomplished those? Through killing? As to be expected. The Federation and Rebellion are not any different when it comes to war, but where the Federation is weak, the Rebellion will stand strong! You have delayed this fight for too long. I doubt you would be capable of taking on a ship as powerful as this!"</text>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_construction">
		<text>We destroyed one of your Flagships back in the Rebel Stronghold. If we did it once, we can do it again.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_3"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_ghostflag">
		<text>We destroyed the original Flagship in the Spectral Wastelands. If we did it once, we can do it again.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_3"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_autodread">
		<text>It's no Flagship, but we destroyed an Auto-Dreadnaught. We can handle anything the Rebellion throws at us.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_3"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_cura">
		<text>It's no Flagship, but we destroyed an advanced W.I. Auto-Cruiser prototype. We can handle anything the Rebellion throws at us.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_3"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_mfkgunboat">
		<text>It's no Flagship, but we destroyed an MFK Gunboat. We can handle anything the Rebellion throws at us.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_3"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="ach_boss_smugglergun">
		<text>It's no Flagship, but we destroyed a stolen Rebel Gunboat. We can handle anything the Rebellion throws at us.</text>
		<event load="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_3"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>We will see about that.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The commander chuckles. "Indeed we will. There will be no peaceful resolution to this confrontation, let us prepare for battle." He cuts comms, and the Flagship continues to charge its weapons.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK_FLAGSHIP"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="BOSS_NEGOTIATE_3">
	<text>"So you are the one responsible for that? Mighty impressive, but that ship was nothing compared to what you're about to face! You will find this ship is far better prepared for a tiny cruiser like yours. Enough delay, you will not escape this fight."</text>
	<variable name="loc_negotiation" op="set" val="1"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK_FLAGSHIP"/>
	</choice>
</event>
	
