<event name="BOSS_FATE_CREW" unique="true">
	<text>A Zoltan ship, here to aid the Federation, hails you. "You are the ship who has come to end this war? Your mission has been all about getting here, the destination. But what you may not realize is the journey here matters so much more. The friends you've made, the alliances you've formed, the people you've saved, together means so much more than this final battle. Tell me, what can you show for your mission after all this time?"</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_ZOLTAN_FIGHT" hostile="false"/>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_ENGI">
		<text>(Engi) We have befriended the Engi.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"The Engi's static emotions means they evaluate all trust on data. You have provided an environment that the Engi has deemed satisfactory, a noble effort. Perhaps this shall aid you, I'm sure your Engi will know how to use it."</text>
			<weapon name="LIST_WEAPONS_ENGI_BOSS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_MANTIS">
		<text>(Mantis) We have befriended the Mantis.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Mantis are not known for their generosity. To have convinced one to work along side you is no easy feat. Perhaps this shall aid you, I'm sure your Mantis will know how to use it."</text>
			<weapon name="LIST_WEAPONS_MANTIS_BOSS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_ROCK">
		<text>(Rockman) We have befriended the Rockmen.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Rockmen are not friendly nor forgiving. To have one working on your ship willingly speaks volumes. Perhaps this shall aid you, I'm sure your Rockman will know how to use it."</text>
			<weapon name="LIST_WEAPONS_ROCK_BOSS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="rock_commando">
		<text>(Lost Sun Commando) We have befriended the Lost Suns.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"The Lost Suns and Federation have always have a thin alliance, and you have helped strengthen it. Perhaps this shall aid you, I'm sure your Commando will know how to use it."</text>
			<weapon name="LIST_WEAPONS_COMMANDO_BOSS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_SLUG">
		<text>(Slugman) We have befriended the Slugs.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"The Slugs, known for their thievery and shifty tactics. You have proven that this stereotype need not stand. Perhaps this shall aid you, I'm sure your Slug will know how to use it."</text>
			<weapon name="LIST_WEAPONS_SLUG_BOSS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="unique_symbiote">
		<text>(Symbiote) We have befriended whatever the hell this thing is.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Ah, I see you have found a way to achieve symbiosis between a Rockman and a Zoltan. How... curious... Er... have this, for achieving something of such a scientific curiosity."</text>
			<weapon name="MISSILES_ENERGY"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>I'm afraid we have nothing to show.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Then you do not deserve to reach your destination. You shall perish in this sector regardless, and so we shall put you out of your misery."</text>
			<ship hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="BOSS_FATE_WEAPONS" unique="true">
	<text>A Lost Sun ship, here to aid the Federation, hails you. "You are the ship who has come to end this war? We have heard legends of your travels. You, of all people, must understand the importance of a weapon. What weapons have the hands of fate bestowed upon your arsenal?"</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_LOSTSUN_FIGHT" hostile="false"/>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_PACIFIST_BOSS">
		<text>(Pacifist Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"I'm afraid that measly thing will not aid you much in the final fight. Have this, in hopes it will be able to carry you to victory. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<weapon name="LIST_WEAPONS_POWERFUL_BOSS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_LASER_BOSS">
		<text>(Laser Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Though common, and rather boring, a laser is a staple weapon in any arsenal. Have this, in hopes it will increase the capabilities of your laser barrage. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="SUPER_AUTO_COOLDOWN"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_ION_BOSS">
		<text>(Ion Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Ions are very much a utility weapon. Now that you are capable of ionizing the enemy defenses, all that's left is to make sure they cannot ionize yours. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="EX_ION_ARMOR"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_BEAM_BOSS">
		<text>(Beam Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Any beam is capable of massive damage to an enemy ship. The only thing that could stand in your way is enemy shields, and this may help with that. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="COMBAT_SHIELDS_JAMMER"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_AMMUNITION_BOSS">
		<text>(Ammunition Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"The enemy defenses will stand no chance while you wield a powerful ballistic weapon. This may help soothe your hunger for more ammunition. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="EX_EXPLOSIVE_REPLICATOR"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_RECYCLER_BOSS">
		<text>(Recycler Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"A recycler weapon, a powerful utility. I see you won't be needing your missiles, so this will help convert them to other, more useful materials. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="RECYCLER_REVERSE"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_CRYSTAL_BOSS">
		<text>(Crystal Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Crystal weapons, belonging to our ancient decendants. Very useful in large quantities, perhaps an extra layer of armor that can provide additional firepower will be of assistance? Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="CRYSTAL_SHARDS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_FIRE_BOSS">
		<text>(Fire Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Ah, a fire weapon. The weapon of choice for the Lost Suns! Glad to see you have embraced the holy fire. You are worthy of this. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="REGEN_ARMOR"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_BIO_BOSS">
		<text>(Anti-Bio Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Deadly and effective, anti-bio weapons are no ample threat. Still, you'll need something to get through their defenses. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<weapon name="LIST_WEAPONS_POWERFUL_BOSS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_FLAK_BOSS">
		<text>(Flak Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Flak cannons excel at taking down shields, but they're worthless if the enemy can evade the projectiles. This should help. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<augment name="COMBAT_ENGINE_JAMMER"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_WEAPONS_ANCIENTS_BOSS">
		<text>(Ancient Weapon) Show them your weapons.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"How... curious. I have never seen a weapon like this, and I have seen many weapons. Surely, with this, the Flagship will stand no chance. Let me repair your hull, to ensure you can make it there to use this gun. Best of luck against the Flagship, captain."</text>
			<damage amount="-30"/>
