<event name="BOSS_CIVILIANS" unique="true">
	<text>A civilian ship is desperately trying to escape from the advancing Rebel fleet, but they've run out of fuel. "Oh thank goodness, we thought all of the Federation ships were busy fighting the Rebels. Please, you know how horrible this sector has become. We need to evacuate while we still can, do you have any fuel to spare?"</text>
