			</item_modify>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Oh thank you Captain. This is why we've always supported the Federation. Just make sure you kill that Flagship so it doesn't all go to waste." The Civilians give you some scrap.</text>
