<event name="BOSS_SLUG_SPECTATOR" unique="true">
	<text>A Slug ship is at this beacon. Their captain appears to be eating some alien version of popcorn. "Oh, well if it isn't the sssship everyone'sss been looking for. I wondered if I'd ssssee you here. Thiss really is ssssuch an interesssssting experience. We have no part to play here, but ssssometimesss you just want to see a good ssshow, you know?"</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Aw crap!-" the Slug is cut off by a Rebel ship flying by. A shot pierces the Slug hull, and the Rebel locks onto you.</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_REBEL_SLUG_SPECTATOR" hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<eventList name="BOSS_SLUG_SPECTATOR_WIN">
	<event>
		<text>It appears the Slug captain is still alive, though his ship and crew are barely holding together. The Slug doesn't seem fazed by the imminent destruction of his ship. "Hah! You sssshowed that Rebel what for. That'ssss what I call entertainment. Though, you can ssssee my ssship won't hold together long, and my crew isss doomed. Perhapsss I will ssstick with you, ssso I can sssssee this ssspectacle all the way to the end."</text>
		<crewMember amount="1" class="slug_saboteur">Rygel</crewMember> <!--used to be Slotz, but that was moved to the slug casino event-->
	</event>
	<event>
